==Dingwaga tsa pereko==
Barolaganyi Seboni o simolotse go bereka ka ngwaga wa 178 e le morutabana mo dikolong tse di kgolwane tsa Mater Spei College, Francistown, gone mo Botswana go fitlha ka ngwaga 1983.MMe e rile go tsweng foo o ne a tlhapiwa kwa Mmadikolo wa lefatshe la Botswana e le modiri wa lekoko le le dirang le tsa ditlhabololo go fitlha ka ngwaga wa 1884.O ne a tswelela ka go atlega mo botselong mme a felela a tlhapiwa e le modiri wa Motlhatlhanyi wa dithuto tse dikgolwane kwa Mmadikolo mme a bowa a atlolosiwa maemo gape go nna yo mogolwane go fitlha ka ngwaga wa 1995<ref>www.bseboni.blogspot.com</ref>.

